<1ST_LINE>u p BC-PP-Dem-Pres-All-SAMPLE     06-06 0850</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-PP-Dem-Pres-All-SAMPLE,400</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>05-31-88 15:17</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the latest, unofficial results in the Democratic
presidential primaries on Tuesday.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>CALIFORNIA</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   0 of 23,613 precincts reporting - 0 percent
   Dukakis, 0 - 0 percent
   Jackson, 0 - 0 percent
