<HEAD>Ford To Bush: Don't Worry About Polls</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Former President Ford said Monday that Vice
President George Bush shouldn't be overly concerned about
presidential public opinion polls showing him running behind
Democrat Michael Dukakis of Massachusetts.
