   That surpassed the previous record weekly point gain of 108.26
set last Dec. 14-18.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by more than 5 to 3 on the
NYSE, with 936 up, 536 down and 482 unchanged. Big Board volume came
to 189.60 million shares, against 193.54 million in the previous
session.
